name: Dr. Andre Hashem
about: Has been teaching and in private practice as a Prosthodontist and leading Cosmetic Dentist in Boston for more than 30 years. In 1990, he completed his prosthodontics specialty degree at Boston University. Dr. Hashem is a Clinical Professor at Boston University School of Dental Medicine and served as the director of the Division of Postdoctoral Prosthodontics from 1999 to 2001. Dr. Hashem's wife, Dr. Christine Lo, is also a prosthodontist with Smile Design Boston.

clinic.name: Smile Design Boston
clinic.description:
We Design Beautiful Smiles
Exceptional Dental Care for You and Your Family
At Smile Design Boston, we offer personalized dental care to all of our patients in a modern and comfortable environment. Our highly trained dental specialists utilize cutting-edge technology to provide an unparalleled experience, catering to services ranging from routine dental cleaning to advanced dental treatments. Conveniently located in downtown Boston, we’re dedicated to helping you achieve the smile you have always wanted.

A Comprehensive Approach to Your Oral Health Care
From preventive care to advanced dental treatments, our expert team offers everything you need to keep your smile healthy and beautiful.

Cosmetic & aesthetic dentistry
➢Teeth cleaning & prevention
➢Invisalign & orthodontics
➢Veneers & crowns
➢Dental implants
➢Periodontal treatment & periodontal plastic surgery
